🧽 Think cleaning is just about looking neat? Nope — it’s way bigger than that. Check out these stats:

📉 U.S. businesses lose $225B+ a year because of sick days tied to poor hygiene.
🧠 75% of clients say cleanliness affects how they see your brand.
🚀 Clean workplaces can bump up productivity by 20%.

Bottom line: being clean is just smart business. 💡 Whether you're running a cozy office or a huge event space, keeping things clean helps your team feel better, your clients stay impressed, and your business run smoother.

That’s where our expert franchisees come in, helping businesses stay clean, safe, and ready for whatever’s next. Let’s keep things fresh – and keep things moving. 💪 

#CommercialCleaning #FirstImpressionsMatter #HealthyWorkplace
